"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">The name format string is used to tell Pymazon how to generate the filename for the downloaded file. A name format string consists of any number of the valid format tags plus any other static text you want included in the filename. </p>\n"
